==Japanese==
===Etymology===
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[卯]] || [[月]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
From either [[卯の花]] (うのはな, ''u no hana''), "the flower of [[w:Deutzia|deutzia]]" or [[卯]] (う, ''u''), "rabbit" + [[月]] (つき, ''tsuki'', "month")

===Noun===
'''卯月''' ([[うづき]], ''uzuki'')

# {{archaic}} the fourth month of the lunar calendar
# {{poetic}} the rabbit month, the month of the [[w:Deutzia|deutzia]]; the month of [[April]]
#: Note: [[卯]] (う, ''u'', "the rabbit"), is the fourth sign of the Chinese Zodiac.

